To fix the unexpected error and complete the implementation, I need to restore the `index.css` file. The version provided in your prompt was truncated, missing the styles for the Flashcards, Saved List, Chat, and the new Google Login components.

I will regenerate the full `index.css` including the styles for the Google Login button and the Auth divider.

# Updated files:

## index.css

Restored missing styles for Home View, Flashcards, Saved List, Chat, and added Google Login styles.

```css
:root {
  /* Light Theme Variables */
  --bg-color: #ffffff;
  --bg-color-secondary: #f5f5f5;
  --text-color: #000000;
  --text-color-secondary: #555555;
  --text-color-muted: #888888;
  --accent-color: #0000ff;
  --border-color: #eee;
  --card-bg: #ffffff;
  --overlay-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);

  --button-bg: #f0f0f0;
  --button-text: #000000;
  --button-hover: #e0e0e0;
  --button-active-bg: #000000;
  --button-active-text: #ffffff;

  --input-bg: transparent;
  --input-border: transparent;

  --header-bg: #f9f9f9;

  --msg-user-bg: #f0f0f0;
  --msg-model-bg: #ffffff;
  --msg-user-text: #000000;
  --msg-model-text: #333333;

  --highlight-color: #eee;
  --success-color: #43a047;
  --error-color: #e53935;
  --warning-color: #cc0000;
  --gold-color: #ffc107;

  --shadow-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  --fab-bg: #000000;
  --fab-text: #ffffff;
}

[data-theme='dark'] {
  /* Dark Theme Variables */
  --bg-color: #121212;
  --bg-color-secondary: #000000;
  --text-color: #e0e0e0;
  --text-color-secondary: #aaaaaa;
  --text-color-muted: #666666;
  --accent-color: #8080ff;
  --border-color: #333333;
  --card-bg: #1e1e1e;
  --overlay-bg: rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.98);

  --button-bg: #333333;
  --button-text: #e0e0e0;
  --button-hover: #444444;
  --button-active-bg: #e0e0e0;
  --button-active-text: #121212;

  --input-bg: #1e1e1e;
  --input-border: #333;

  --header-bg: #252525;

  --msg-user-bg: #333333;
  --msg-model-bg: #1e1e1e;
  --msg-user-text: #e0e0e0;
  --msg-model-text: #e0e0e0;

  --highlight-color: #333;
  --warning-color: #ff6666;

  --shadow-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  --fab-bg: #ffffff;
  --fab-text: #000000;
}

@keyframes blink {
  from, to { opacity: 1 }
  50% { opacity: 0; }
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

body {
  background-color: var(--bg-color);
  color: var(--text-color);
  font-family: 'Kosugi', sans-serif;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 2rem;
  transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
}
#root {
  max-width: 65ch;
  margin: auto;
  position: relative;
  min-height: 90vh;
}
h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
  font-size: 1em;
  margin: 0;
  font-weight: normal;
}
button {
  background: none;
  border: none;
  padding: 0;
  font: inherit;
  color: inherit;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.interactive-word {
  color: var(--text-color);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.2s ease-in-out;
}
.interactive-word:hover {
  color: var(--accent-color);
  text-decoration: underline;
}

.ascii-art {
  font-family: monospace;
  text-align: left;
  white-space: pre;
  color: var(--text-color-muted);
  margin: 2rem 0;
  line-height: 1.1;
  font-size: 0.8em;
}
.blinking-cursor {
  animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
}

/* Search Bar Styles */
.search-container {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  width: 100%;
}

.search-form {
  flex-grow: 1;
}

.search-input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 0.5rem 0.2rem;
  font: inherit;
  color: inherit;
  border: none;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  background-color: var(--input-bg);
  box-sizing: border-box;
  outline: none;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.search-input:focus {
  border-color: var(--text-color);
}

.search-input:disabled {
  color: var(--text-color-secondary);
}

.search-input::placeholder {
  color: var(--text-color-muted);
  opacity: 1;
}

.theme-toggle-btn {
  background: none;
  border: none;
  padding: 0.5rem;
  color: var(--text-color);
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  border-radius: 50%;
  transition: background 0.2s;
  position: relative;
}
.theme-toggle-btn:hover {
  background: var(--button-bg);
}
.theme-toggle-btn.active-user {
  color: var(--accent-color);
}
.user-dot {
  position: absolute;
  top: 4px;
  right: 4px;
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  background-color: var(--success-color);
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 1px solid var(--bg-color);
}

/* Autocomplete Dropdown */
.suggestions-dropdown {
  position: absolute;
  top: 100%;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  background-color: var(--card-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  border-top: none;
  border-radius: 0 0 4px 4px;
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 6px var(--shadow-color);
  z-index: 100;
  max-height: 250px; 
  overflow-y: auto;
}

.suggestion-item {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
  text-align: left;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  color: var(--text-color);
  cursor: pointer;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  font-size: 1rem;
}

.suggestion-item:hover {
  background-color: var(--highlight-color);
}
.suggestion-item:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

/* Wiki Page Sections */
.wiki-content {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  padding-bottom: 3rem;
}

.wiki-intro {
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.wiki-section {
  border-left: 2px solid var(--border-color);
  padding-left: 1.5rem;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.wiki-section:hover {
  border-left-color: var(--text-color-secondary);
}

.wiki-section-title {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--text-color-muted);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.wiki-section-body p {
  margin: 0;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* Nav Buttons */
.nav-controls {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.2rem;
}

.nav-btn {
  padding: 0.4rem;
  color: var(--text-color);
  border-radius: 4px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  transition: background 0.2s;
}

.nav-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background: var(--button-bg);
}

.nav-btn:disabled {
  color: var(--text-color-muted);
  cursor: default;
  opacity: 0.5;
}

/* Home View Styles */
.home-view {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    gap: 3rem;
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out;
}

.app-title-large {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.home-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 300px;
}

.home-btn {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 30px;
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    color: var(--text-color);
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px var(--shadow-color);
}

.home-btn:hover {
    background-color: var(--button-hover);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px var(--shadow-color);
}

.home-btn:active {
    transform: translateY(0);
}

/* AI FAB */
.ai-fab {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 2rem;
    right: 2rem;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--fab-bg);
    color: var(--fab-text);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px var(--shadow-color);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    z-index: 1000;
}

.ai-fab:hover {
    transform: scale(1.1);
}

.save-toggle-button {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--text-color-secondary);
    transition: all 0.2s;
}
.save-toggle-button.saved {
    background-color: var(--text-color);
    color: var(--bg-color);
    border-color: var(--text-color);
}

/* Saved Words Overlay */
.saved-list-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: var(--overlay-bg);
    z-index: 2000;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
}

.saved-list-container {
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 500px;
    height: 80vh;
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px var(--shadow-color);
    position: relative;
}

.saved-list-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.saved-list-header h3 {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
}

.close-button {
    color: var(--text-color-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
}
.close-button:hover {
    color: var(--text-color);
}

.backup-controls {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.backup-btn {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 4px;
}
.backup-btn:hover {
    background-color: var(--button-bg);
}

.sort-controls {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-color-secondary);
    overflow-x: auto;
    padding-bottom: 5px;
}
.sort-btn {
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--text-color-muted);
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    white-space: nowrap;
}
.sort-btn.active {
    color: var(--text-color);
    border-color: var(--border-color);
    font-weight: bold;
}

.saved-words-ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    overflow-y: auto;
    flex-grow: 1;
}

.saved-word-item {
    padding: 0.8rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
}

.word-button {
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
}
.word-button:hover {
    color: var(--accent-color);
}

.edit-mode-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    width: 100%;
}
.edit-word-input {
    flex-grow: 1;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    padding: 0.2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background-color: var(--input-bg);
    color: var(--text-color);
}
.delete-btn-edit-mode {
    background-color: var(--error-color);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
}

.mastery-indicator {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3px;
    margin-top: 4px;
}
.mastery-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: #eee;
}

.header-undo-btn {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
    text-decoration: underline;
}

.undo-toast {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 1rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background-color: var(--text-color);
    color: var(--bg-color);
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 30px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px var(--shadow-color);
    z-index: 10;
}
.undo-btn {
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--gold-color);
}

.delete-history-btn {
    color: var(--text-color-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    margin-left: 0.5rem;
}
.delete-history-btn:hover {
    color: var(--error-color);
}
.star-btn-list {
    color: var(--text-color-muted);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    padding: 0.2rem;
}
.star-btn-list.active {
    color: var(--gold-color);
}

/* Chat Overlay */
.chat-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 5rem;
    right: 2rem;
    width: 350px;
    height: 500px;
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px var(--shadow-color);
    z-index: 1500;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
}

.chat-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
}

.chat-header {
    padding: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: var(--header-bg);
    border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
}

.chat-messages {
    flex-grow: 1;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.8rem;
}

.message {
    padding: 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    max-width: 85%;
}

.message.user {
    align-self: flex-end;
    background-color: var(--msg-user-bg);
    color: var(--msg-user-text);
}

.message.model {
    align-self: flex-start;
    background-color: var(--msg-model-bg);
    color: var(--msg-model-text);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
}

.chat-input-area {
    padding: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
}

.chat-input {
    flex-grow: 1;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background-color: var(--input-bg);
    color: var(--text-color);
}

.chat-send-btn {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background-color: var(--text-color);
    color: var(--bg-color);
    border-radius: 4px;
}

/* Flashcard Styles */
.flashcard-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
    z-index: 1000;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

.flashcard-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 500px;
    height: 90vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
}

.flashcard-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.mode-toggle {
    display: flex;
    background-color: var(--button-bg);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 2px;
}

.mode-toggle button {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 18px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-color-secondary);
}

.mode-toggle button.active {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    color: var(--text-color);
    box-shadow: 0 1px 3px var(--shadow-color);
}

/* Card Flip Logic */
.card {
    flex-grow: 1;
    perspective: 1000px;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.card-inner {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    transition: transform 0.6s;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px var(--shadow-color);
    border-radius: 16px;
}

.card.flipped .card-inner {
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
}

.card-front, .card-back {
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding: 2rem;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    overflow-y: auto;
}

.card-back {
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: flex-start;
    text-align: left;
}

.card-word {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-align: center;
}
.card-word-small {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin: 0;
}
.card-instruction {
    color: var(--text-color-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
}

.card-header-back {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.save-icon-btn {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-color-muted);
}
.save-icon-btn.saved {
    color: var(--gold-color);
}

/* Collapsible Sections in Flashcard */
.collapsible-section {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
}
.section-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    cursor: pointer;
}
.section-header h4 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-color-secondary);
}
.section-content {
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
}
.arrow {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-color-muted);
}
.refresh-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
}

/* Controls */
.flashcard-controls {
    height: 80px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
}

.reveal-btn, .next-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem;
    background-color: var(--text-color);
    color: var(--bg-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
}

.srs-buttons.simple {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    width: 100%;
}

.srs-btn {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
}

.srs-btn.know {
    background-color: var(--success-color);
}
.srs-btn.dont-know {
    background-color: var(--error-color);
}

/* Auth Modal Styles */
.auth-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: var(--overlay-bg);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    z-index: 2000;
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
}

.auth-container {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 400px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px var(--shadow-color);
    position: relative;
}

.auth-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.auth-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.auth-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
}

.auth-input {
    padding: 0.8rem;
    background-color: var(--input-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    color: var(--text-color);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: inherit;
}

.auth-input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--text-color);
}

.auth-btn {
    padding: 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    transition: all 0.2s;
}

.auth-btn.primary {
    background-color: var(--text-color);
    color: var(--bg-color);
    border: 1px solid var(--text-color);
}

.auth-btn.primary:hover:not(:disabled) {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--text-color);
}

.auth-btn.primary:disabled {
    opacity: 0.7;
    cursor: wait;
}

.auth-btn.logout {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--error-color);
    color: var(--error-color);
}
.auth-btn.logout:hover {
    background-color: var(--error-color);
    color: white;
}

.auth-footer {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
